Kolawale Ojeleke aka Zion Century was recently awarded the most talented artiste of the year at the 2020 edition of the Esteem Awards. The artiste couldn’t contain his joy as he kept smiling with the honour. Zion century says he is honoured to be placed in such distinguished ranks as those of the past honorees. He also used the opportunity to appreciate everyone that has contributed to the success of his song as well as the organisers of the Esteem Awards for the honour. Since the release of his song, ‘Overload’ in December 2020, the song has gained lots of attention all over the world, including making it to the Top Ten Hit songs in Australia.